    <item>
      <title>How to run a website recovery &#34;fire drill.&#34;</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/2015/10/01/how-to-run-a-website-recovery-fire-drill./</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Oct 2015 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/2015/10/01/how-to-run-a-website-recovery-fire-drill./</guid>
      <description>

&lt;p&gt;Do you have a plan for a potential website outage? Do you know if it works? Without verification your plan is only a hunch. You can choose to verify your plan on your own, on purpose, in controlled circumstances; or while your site is down during the biggest day of your career. Having a plan is only half of the equation. Learn how to test your response plan on your own terms, by planning and executing “fire drills.”&lt;/p&gt;

